Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.93,0:11:10.60,DefaultItalicsTop,Takachiho,0,0,0,,{All right, you good little old dudes! \NHow are you doing?}Này, những lão già vẫn khoẻ chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.61,0:11:13.40,DefaultItalicsTop,Takachiho,0,0,0,,{It's me, Miss Takachiho!}Là ta Takachiho đây!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.61,0:11:14.36,Default,Kawado,0,0,0,,{This is when the }{\i1}{Me and Old Dudes}{\i0}{ rerun airs.}Đúng lúc chiếu chương trình này luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.36,0:11:15.95,Default,Kawado,0,0,0,,{Wanna watch with me?}Xem cùng tao nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.82,0:11:24.19,DefaultItalicsTop,Old Dude,0,0,0,,{Ow! Help! Mommy!}Mẹ ơi cứu con!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.30,0:11:26.52,DefaultItalics,Nekohira,0,0,0,,{Huh... Something about this is familiar.}Ủa? Có gì đó thân quen...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.87,0:11:28.50,DefaultItalicsTop,Old Dudes,0,0,0,,{What the hell?!}Cái quái gì vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.43,0:11:29.99,DefaultItalics,Nekohira,0,0,0,,{Actually, I think I was there...}Cơ mà hình như ta từng ở đây...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.50,0:11:30.38,DefaultItalicsTop,Old Dudes,0,0,0,,{Is this for real?! Or a prank?!}Là thật hả? Hay đang đùa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.68,0:11:33.88,DefaultItalicsTop,Takachiho,0,0,0,,{Now then, everyone, let's all quiet down!}Mọi người im lặng nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.20,0:11:38.39,DefaultItalicsTop,Takachiho,0,0,0,,{Today, we're going to keep playing \Nuntil there's only one of you left.}Hôm nay chúng ta sẽ chơi đến người cuối cùng.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.39,0:11:44.81,DefaultItalics,Nekohira,0,0,0,,{I fought there, and then... those ninja...}Ta đã chiến đấu ở đó... và sau đó tên ninja...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.43,0:11:46.61,DefaultItalics,Nekohira,0,0,0,,{killed me!}đã giết ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.06,0:11:54.35,DefaultItalics,Nekohira,0,0,0,,{But... why am I a cat?}Nhưng tại sao ta lại là mèo?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.85,0:11:58.34,DefaultItalics,Nekohira,0,0,0,,Hình như là...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.08,0:12:03.41,Flashback,Researcher,0,0,0,,{Hello there, son. I take it you're awake?}Xin chào, cậu tỉnh rồi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.41,0:12:06.52,Flashback,Researcher,0,0,0,,{It's quite impressive that \Nyou managed to survive}Không ngờ cậu có thể sống sót
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.52,0:12:11.18,Flashback,Researcher,0,0,0,,{against our Rainbow Hound \Nuntil the very end.}qua cái chương trình Rainbow Hound đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.79,0:12:17.72,Flashback,Researcher,0,0,0,,{Out of respect for your tenacity, \Nwe've kept a portion of your brain intact.}Vì tôn trọng sự kiên trì của cậu nên \Nbọn ta sẽ giữ nguyên một phần bộ não
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.21,0:12:22.26,Flashback,Researcher,0,0,0,,{We've had real trouble with \Nmortality rates post-transplant...}Chúng tôi đang gặp rắc rối với \Ntỉ lệ tự vong sau cấy ghép...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.69,0:12:24.82,Flashback,Researcher,0,0,0,,{So we have big hopes for you!}Thế nên kì vọng cậu lắm đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.37,0:12:40.98,DefaultItalics,Nekohira,0,0,0,,{So my brain...}Vậy ra não của mình...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.43,0:12:45.70,DefaultItalics,Nekohira,0,0,0,,{was transplanted into this cat?}đã bị chuyển vào con mèo này?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.06,0:12:50.71,Default,Kawado,0,0,0,,{Huh? Kuro-kun?}Ủa? Kuro à?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.08,0:12:52.95,Default,Kawado,0,0,0,,{Aren't you back kinda early?}Sao về sớm thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.58,0:12:56.43,Default,Kuro,0,0,0,,{I was sleepy, so I left early.}Buồn ngủ quá nên về.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.43,0:12:58.09,Default,Kawado,0,0,0,,{On your first day?!}Mới ngày đầu mà!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.53,0:13:02.72,Default,Kawado,0,0,0,,Biết là không thích đi học nhưng đừng để bị đuổi đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.72,0:13:05.97,Default,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Well, who knows what'll happen?}Vâng, mà cũng chả biết.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.94,0:13:07.97,DefaultItalics,Nekohira,0,0,0,,{This guy...}Tên này...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.43,0:13:17.47,DefaultItalics,Nekohira,0,0,0,,{He's the one who killed me!}Là kẻ đã giết mình!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.49,0:13:25.08,Default,Kawado,0,0,0,,{Huh? Shinobu, what's got you so upset?}Shinobu? Sao mày lại cảnh giác thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.08,0:13:30.50,Default,Kawado,0,0,0,,{Oh, Kuro-kun, if you're bored, \Nwhy don't we drink in Ono-san's room?}A Kuro, nếu rảnh thì ghé\N nhà lão Ono làm tí bia nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.50,0:13:33.93,DefaultItalics,Nekohira,0,0,0,,{Wait, I could've sworn \NI was thinking something...}Ủa? Ta đây vừa nghĩ gì thế nhỉ...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.11,0:13:41.26,Default,Kawado,0,0,0,,{Kuro-kun?}Kuro?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.64,0:13:43.55,Default,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Oh... Sure.}À vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.45,0:13:49.02,Default,Kato,0,0,0,,{You've made it home safely,}Về nhà an toàn rồi nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.51,0:13:50.65,Default,Kato,0,0,0,,Onikobe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.26,0:13:54.52,Default,Onikobe,0,0,0,,{Sir! The new recruit relieved me of duty.}Vâng! Tôi đã được miễn nhiệm khỏi vai trò.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.39,0:13:58.41,Default,Onikobe,0,0,0,,Chiến trường tiếp theo là ở đâu ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:01.78,Default,Kato,0,0,0,,{Your next battlefield...}Chiến trường tiếp theo...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.74,0:14:04.66,Default,Kato,0,0,0,,{is right here.}là ở đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.69,0:14:11.29,DefaultItalics,Eita,0,0,0,,{The first day since the \Nbullies were dealt with...}Ngày đầu tiên đi học không bị bắt nạt...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.81,0:14:13.92,DefaultItalics,Eita,0,0,0,,{It's like a whole new world.}Cứ như một thế giới mới.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.92,0:14:17.97,DefaultItalics,Eita,0,0,0,,{Azuma made some excuse about being \Nhospitalized, like a politician would...}Azuma có vẻ phải nhập viện...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.97,0:14:20.08,DefaultItalics,Eita,0,0,0,,{And I don't see Noheji, either.}Mình cũng không thấy Noheji.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.08,0:14:23.68,DefaultItalics,Eita,0,0,0,,{Kuro-san also isn't here, for some reason...}Kuro cũng không đi học vì lý do gì đó...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:27.15,DefaultItalics,Eita,0,0,0,,{And everyone believes I kicked their asses.}Những kẻ bắt nạt mình đã biến mất.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.15,0:14:29.67,DefaultItalics,Eita,0,0,0,,{I think my life might \Nactually be turning around!}Cuộc sống học đường sẽ quay lại!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.67,0:14:31.22,DefaultItalics,Eita,0,0,0,,{Maybe I'll become popular?!}Có thể mình sẽ nổi tiếng!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:34.42,DefaultItalics,Eita,0,0,0,,{Ow...}Đau...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.33,0:14:39.69,Default,Noheji,0,0,0,,{Hey. Mind if I have a word?}Mày đi cùng tao nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.21,0:14:49.78,DefaultItalics,Eita,0,0,0,,{This has gotta be payback \Nfor yesterday, right?}Quả nhiên là trả thù vụ hôm qua?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.78,0:14:51.00,Default,Noheji,0,0,0,,Eita.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.57,0:14:58.71,Default,Noheji,0,0,0,,{Please! You've gotta bring that \Ntransfer student, Kuro-san, around.}Làm ơn! Hãy dẫn học sinh\N chuyển trường đó đến cho tao!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.34,0:15:04.03,Default,Noheji,0,0,0,,{It's like... I know he's the \None who actually hit me,}Cảm giác như... đứa đánh tao là nó,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.03,0:15:06.84,Default,Noheji,0,0,0,,{and he... Kuro-san...}và nó... à không, Kuro
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.84,0:15:09.75,Default,Noheji,0,0,0,,{is one of those folks you're not \Nsupposed to talk about in this country.}là một trong những kẻ không\N được nhắc đến ở đất nước này.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.75,0:15:11.10,Default,Noheji,0,0,0,,{He's a ninja, isn't he?!}Cậu ta là Ninja phải không?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.10,0:15:12.92,DefaultItalics,Eita,0,0,0,,{You just said it out loud.}Nói thẳng ra luôn còn gì...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.92,0:15:17.10,Default,Noheji,0,0,0,,{And he's probably staying at \Nyour house for some reason, right?}Và vì vài lí do nên đang ở nhà mày, phải không?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.10,0:15:18.75,Default,Eita,0,0,0,,{Not exactly...}Không hẳn...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.75,0:15:21.11,Default,Noheji,0,0,0,,{Please! You've gotta help me meet Kuro-san!}Làm ơn! Hãy giúp tao gặp cậu ấy!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.11,0:15:23.47,Default,Eita,0,0,0,,{Come on, I don't know \Nwhat you expect me to—}Không không, dù có nói thế thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.47,0:15:24.44,Default,Kuro,0,0,0,,{What's up?}Cái gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.61,0:15:27.08,Default,Eita,0,0,0,,{You were here?!}Cậu ở đây à?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.19,0:15:33.62,Default,Noheji,0,0,0,,{You kicked my ass like it was nothing! \NAnd I have a request!}Cậu đã hạ tôi trong một nốt nhạc!\N Tôi có một điều muốn nhờ!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.08,0:15:37.00,DefaultItalics,Eita,0,0,0,,{Not happening...}Không được đâu...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.80,0:15:41.25,Default,Noeheji,0,0,0,,{Will you help me in a fight against \Nsome guys from another school?!}Liệu có thể giúp tôi xử lý \Nđám trường bên được không?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.95,0:15:44.49,DefaultItalics,Eita,0,0,0,,{Kuro-san's got an exclusive contract with me.}Kuro đã kí hợp đồng với mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.49,0:15:45.53,Default,Kuro,0,0,0,,{What are the details?}Nói thử xem.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.39,0:15:48.39,Default,Eita,0,0,0,,{You're gonna hear him out?}Nghe à?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.69,0:15:59.03,Default,Ono,0,0,0,,{Kuro-kun's actually at school.}Kuro đang đi học rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.17,0:16:03.92,Default,Kato,0,0,0,,{Aw, that's a problem. \NThis package is actually perishable.}Chà chà, tôi đang định giao hàng.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.92,0:16:06.21,Default,Ono,0,0,0,,{Oh, I can hold it for him, then.}Vậy để tôi giữ cho.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.21,0:16:08.77,Default,Ono,0,0,0,,{He doesn't have a refrigerator, anyway.}Cậu ta không có tủ lạnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.77,0:16:10.04,Default,Kato,0,0,0,,{You're a lifesaver!}Cảm ơn chú.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.38,0:16:11.65,Default,Kato,0,0,0,,{Can I get your stamp?}Chú đóng dấu vào đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.65,0:16:14.04,Default,Ono,0,0,0,,{Uh, one second...}Chờ chút...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.09,0:16:17.04,Default,Kato,0,0,0,,{I really appreciate it.}Cảm ơn ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:20.83,Default,Ono,0,0,0,,{Now, where did I put that thing?}Bỏ đâu rồi nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.06,0:16:45.32,Default,Kato,0,0,0,,{You've been living here longer than \Nanyone else in the building, right?}Chú sống ở căn hộ này lâu nhất nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.32,0:16:49.20,Default,Ono,0,0,0,,{Hate to admit it, but it \Nreally is like home to me...}Ừm thì... nó cứ như ngôi nhà của tôi vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.20,0:16:52.70,Default,Kato,0,0,0,,{I'm curious, when did Kumogakure-san move in?}Cơ mà Kumogakure chuyển vào khi nào?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.39,0:16:57.25,Default,Ono,0,0,0,,{Kuro-kun kinda forced his way in...}Kuro thì hình như...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.25,0:17:02.75,Default,Ono,0,0,0,,{Huh? Feels kinda like it was pretty recent, \Nbut also like he's always been there...}Ủa? Cảm giác như gần đây... hay là rất lâu rồi nhỉ...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.75,0:17:03.48,Default,Ono,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Ủa?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.48,0:17:06.77,DefaultItalics,Kato,0,0,0,,{He's been hypnotized.}Lão này đã bị thôi miên.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.39,0:17:11.98,DefaultItalics,Kato,0,0,0,,{Controlled so that his memories \Nof Kumogakure are hazy.}Kumogakure đã kiểm soát tâm trí của lão ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.47,0:17:27.36,Default,Noheji,0,0,0,,{Thanks to my dad, I grew up reading \N}{\i1}{Gorillaman}{\i0}{ and }{\i1}{Be-Bop}{\i0}{, stuff like that.}Nhờ ông già nên tôi hay đọc Gorillaman và Bebop...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.70,0:17:28.89,Default,Kuro,0,0,0,,{I read those, too.}Tôi cũng đọc nè.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.89,0:17:31.36,Default,Noheji,0,0,0,,{Really?! They're pretty great, right?}Vậy à? Nó hay mà nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.36,0:17:34.54,Default,Noheji,0,0,0,,{So, I've always looked up \Nto Yankee-style punks...}Thế nên tôi ngưỡng mộ phong cách yankee...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.54,0:17:38.62,Default,Noheji,0,0,0,,{But as I'm sure you know, \Nthey're kind of an endangered species.}Nhưng cậu biết rồi đó, \Nphong cách đó gần như tuyệt chủng.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.09,0:17:42.12,Default,Noheji,0,0,0,,{A brawl with guys from another school... \NI figured that was just a dream.}Một cuộc ẩu đả với đám trường khác, cứ như mơ vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.46,0:17:46.63,Default,Noheji,0,0,0,,{So I was picking on weaklings instead, \Nwhich is in no way satisfying.}Để tránh nhàm chán thì tôi đành\N bắt nạt mấy đứa yếu đuối.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.63,0:17:49.63,DefaultItalics,Eita,0,0,0,,{\i0}{That}{\i1}{ was the reason I was being bullied?}Lý do mình bị bắt nạt đó à?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.63,0:17:52.13,Default,Kuro,0,0,0,,Thế giờ sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.13,0:17:56.14,Default,Noheji,0,0,0,,{It turns out there's a \Nmissing link here in Nerima.}Có một liên kết bị thiếu ở Nerima này.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.53,0:17:58.64,Default,Noheji,0,0,0,,{A regular coelacanth high school!}Một trường cao trung cá biệt.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.84,0:18:01.19,Default,Kuro,0,0,0,,{And where is it?}Thế nó ở đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.19,0:18:02.62,Default,Noheji,0,0,0,,{The Nerima Ward School...}Quận Nerima...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.13,0:18:04.85,Default,Noheji,0,0,0,,{Yankii High!}Cao trung Yankii.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.23,0:18:13.12,Default,Kato,0,0,0,,{Onikobe, what did you find \Nin Kumogakure's room?}Onikobe, cô tìm thấy gì trong phòng Kumogakure?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.12,0:18:18.74,Default,Onikobe,0,0,0,,{Sir, the tea table he had was \Nan auto-deploying defense shield.}Vâng, một bàn trà có khả năng như khiên chắn.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.15,0:18:21.43,Default,Onikobe,0,0,0,,{Also, installed beneath his floor}Phía dưới chiếu,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.43,0:18:24.79,Default,Onikobe,0,0,0,,{was a shelter capable of \Nwithstanding a bunker buster.}là một nơi trú ẩn có thể\N chống được tấn công bằng bom.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.73,0:18:29.92,Default,Onikobe,0,0,0,,{I believe the building itself \Nstill has more secrets.}Tôi tin rằng vẫn còn nhiều bí ẩn\Ntrong căn chung cư đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.42,0:18:34.27,Default,Onikobe,0,0,0,,{Escape would be able to destroy it. \NI don't think it poses any real threat.}Escape có thể phá huỷ nó. \NTôi không nghĩ đó là vấn đề.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.78,0:18:37.56,Default,Kato,0,0,0,,{What about the other residents?}Còn những cư dân khác?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.51,0:18:40.18,Default,Onikobe,0,0,0,,{They're normal civilians, sir.}Dân thường ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.18,0:18:42.65,Default,Onikobe,0,0,0,,{I'd have them under control in three minutes.}Tôi có thể hạ họ trong dưới 3 phút.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.19,0:18:46.38,Default,Kato,0,0,0,,{You think that too, huh?}Cô cũng nghĩ thế à?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.38,0:18:49.69,Default,Kato,0,0,0,,{I'll admit, going into that building, \Neven I tend to lower my guard.}Tôi cũng vậy, khi vào căn\N chung cư đó đã không cảnh giác.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.69,0:18:51.73,Default,Kato,0,0,0,,{Rather, it's set up in a way \Nto make me lower it.}Không, nó khiến tôi mất cảnh giác.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.41,0:18:54.65,Default,Kato,0,0,0,,{They're so easygoing, it's unnatural.}Bọn họ là những người dễ tính, quá bất thường.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.65,0:18:56.78,Default,Kato,0,0,0,,{They don't betray any kind of presence...}Họ không nghi ngờ bất cứ thứ gì...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.78,0:18:59.06,Default,Kato,0,0,0,,{The same way a jonin would.}Cứ như những ninja cấp cao vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.83,0:19:01.95,Default,Onikobe,0,0,0,,{You think they're Kumogakure's bodyguards?}Là hộ vệ của Kumogakure ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.40,0:19:06.49,Default,Kato,0,0,0,,{Can't tell. But we're at war.}Không biết, nhưng chúng ta đang trong chiến tranh.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.49,0:19:08.96,Default,Kato,0,0,0,,{There's no telling what might happen.}Không biết điều gì có thể xảy ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.45,0:19:14.26,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{What? You need something?}Gì? Cần gì à?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.26,0:19:15.48,Default,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Hey, Hibi.}Hibi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.48,0:19:18.70,Default,Kuro,0,0,0,,Bọn này sẽ tấn công đám cao\N trung Yankii, cậu tham gia không?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.70,0:19:19.97,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{Oh, hell yeah.}Đi đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.97,0:19:20.97,DefaultItalics,Eita,0,0,0,,{So casual?!}Dễ tính vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.97,0:19:25.10,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{More importantly, did the school \Nget hit with a laser yesterday?}Cơ mà hôm qua có ai trong trường dính laze à?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.10,0:19:28.10,Default,Kuro,0,0,0,,{It was Escape. I called in fire support.}Tôi gọi hỗ trợ đấy, là Escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.10,0:19:29.74,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{Are you shitting me?}Đùa nhau à?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.38,0:19:33.23,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{That's top secret ninja tech, \Nand you made the call?}Cậu gọi được vũ khí tối thượng của ninja?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.59,0:19:36.78,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{I can dodge lightning, but not that bad boy.}Tôi có thể né được nó nhưng tên đó thì không.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.78,0:19:38.98,Default,Kuro,0,0,0,,{The lightning }{\i1}{did}{\i0}{ hit you, though.}Cậu từng bị sét đánh trúng mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:42.74,Default,Noheji,0,0,0,,{I hate to interrupt, but...}Xin lỗi vì xen ngang...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.30,0:19:45.77,Default,Noheji,0,0,0,,{Are you the legendary delinquent \Nwho single-handedly beat}Cậu có phải là tên du côn huyền thoại tay không
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.77,0:19:48.27,Default,Noheji,0,0,0,,{the ass of every punk in Nerima \Nand eastern Tokyo,}xử lý đám giang hồ ở Nerima và khu\N phía Đông Tokyo không?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.75,0:19:50.69,Default,Noheji,0,0,0,,{Thunder Hibi-san?!}Hibi thần sấm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.84,0:19:53.99,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{So you've heard of me.}Nghe danh rồi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.77,0:19:55.99,Default,Noheji,0,0,0,,{This is awesome!}Quá dữ!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.99,0:19:58.38,Default,Noheji,0,0,0,,{You were my hero in elementary school!}Cậu là anh hùng tôi ngưỡng mộ hồi tiểu học đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.11,0:20:01.89,Default,Noheji,0,0,0,,{Wait... What are you doing \Nin this school, though?}Ủa? Sao lại vào học trường này?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.89,0:20:04.87,Default,Noheji,0,0,0,,{You'd have to be a fair bit older...}Cứ tưởng cậu phải lớn tuổi lắm chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.34,0:20:07.82,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{It's part of the job.}Nhiệm vụ thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.82,0:20:09.27,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{I wouldn't ask any more questions.}Đừng hỏi gì nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.27,0:20:11.09,Default,Noheji,0,0,0,,{Right! You got it!}Vâng! Đã rõ!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.46,0:20:13.27,DefaultItalics,Eita,0,0,0,,{What is with these people?}Bọn này bị gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.27,0:20:15.59,DefaultItalics,Eita,0,0,0,,{They're making it super obvious \Nthat they're ninja.}Tự khoe mình là ninja luôn à?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.59,0:20:19.13,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{But Kuro, if they let you use Escape,}Nhưng Kuro, nếu họ để cậu dùng Escape,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.13,0:20:22.66,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{then this mission is probably a lot \Nmore dangerous than we thought.}tức là nhiệm vụ này nguy hiểm hơn rồi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.90,0:20:25.16,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{What's going on?}Chuyện gì đang xảy ra?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.16,0:20:28.67,Default,Kuro,0,0,0,,{I have no clue, but command \Nwouldn't give a second thought}Không biết nhưng cấp trên nghĩ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.67,0:20:31.47,Default,Kuro,0,0,0,,{to blowing the whole school away.}sẽ thổi bay ngôi trường này nếu cần.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.03,0:20:35.30,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{We're looking at a second \N22-2-22 incident, then...}Chúng ta đang trong thời khắc thảm hoạ 22-2-22 à...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.42,0:20:40.76,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{You know, though,}Cơ mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.76,0:20:44.44,Default,Hibi,0,0,0,,{I wish we had a reason to raid these guys\Nrather than it being totally random.}Tôi muốn có lý do gì đó tấn công\N chúng nó hơn là tự nhiên đến...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.81,0:20:48.95,Default,Noheji,0,0,0,,{In terms of motivation for brawls, \Nsomeone's girl being stolen is a big one.}Nói về động cơ thì... quả nhiên là gái.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.41,0:20:53.94,Default,Kuro,0,0,0,,{I was wondering, who's that girl \Nwho had you carrying the box, Eita?}Cơ mà cô gái bảo cậu mang cái hộp giùm đó là ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.08,0:20:56.94,Default,Eita,0,0,0,,{Yamada-san?}Yamada á?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.81,0:20:59.27,Default,Noheji,0,0,0,,{That's her.}Là cô ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.27,0:21:03.62,Default,Noheji,0,0,0,,{She's the prettiest girl in school, \Nbut she's kinda... Well, just look at her.}Tuy là cô gái xinh đẹp nhất trường nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.19,0:21:06.95,Default,Noheji,0,0,0,,{Makes people tend to keep their distance.}Khiến không ai muốn tiếp cận.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.95,0:21:09.56,DefaultItalics,Eita,0,0,0,,{Ew, she's eating her boogers.}Ăn cứt mũi kìa...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.56,0:21:14.46,Default,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Boogers are actually a natural \Nsupplement, rich in vitamin D.}Ăn cứt mũi cung cấp nhiều vitamin D lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.46,0:21:15.61,Default,Kuro,0,0,0,,{I'm impressed.}Đỉnh đấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.02,0:21:18.46,Default,Eita,0,0,0,,{You're lying. I know you're lying.}Đừng có đùa. Đừng có giỡn!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.46,0:21:21.97,Default,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Do you really think she'll cooperate?}Cơ mà cô ta sẽ hợp tác chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.29,0:21:24.47,Default,Kuro,0,0,0,,{By letting those punks get on her case.}Để bọn du côn đụng tay vào cô ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.98,0:21:31.46,Default,Noheji,0,0,0,,{She says it's okay.}Cô ấy bảo được.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.46,0:21:32.48,Default,Eita,0,0,0,,{That was fast!}Nhanh quá!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.95,0:21:39.24,DefaultItalics,Eita,0,0,0,,{They said to put my hair in a pompadour \Nsince we're going to Yankii High...}Họ nói mình nên để quả đầu du côn\Nvì phải tấn công vào trường Yankii...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.66,0:21:41.49,DefaultItalics,Eita,0,0,0,,{But I don't wanna.}Chẳng muốn chút nào...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.35,0:21:45.12,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,{Ei-chan! How's your mom been?}Ei-chan! Mẹ vẫn khoẻ chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.45,0:21:47.74,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,{I heard you're going back to school!}Nghe nói cháu quay lại trường rồi hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.74,0:21:48.69,Default,Eita,0,0,0,,{Yeah...}Vâng...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.69,0:21:50.75,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,{Oh, pomade, huh?}A, keo vuốt tóc?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.16,0:21:54.82,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,{Back in school, feeling saucy... \NGot a date or something?}Quay lại trường, chỉnh sửa tóc tai... hẹn hò hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.25,0:21:59.13,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,{Well, you make sure to take care \Nof your mother, Ei-chan!}Nhớ chăm sóc mẹ chu đáo nhé, Ei-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.13,0:22:01.63,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,{Thanks, come again!}Cảm ơn rất nhiều!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.94,0:22:05.64,DefaultItalics,Eita,0,0,0,,{I seriously have no idea what \Nthat lady's deal is.}Bà già đó là sao vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.64,0:22:08.77,DefaultItalics,Eita,0,0,0,,{I've asked Mom about her \Nand she says she doesn't know.}Mình đã hỏi mẹ mà bà ấy có biết đâu...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.39,0:22:10.88,DefaultItalics,Eita,0,0,0,,{Just who is she?}Bà đó là ai vậy?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.99,0:24:10.01,Signs_EpTitle,Kuro,0,0,0,,{\q2\pos(602,295)\fscx85\3c&H3B673C&\c&HDAFEDF&\4c&H416C45&\shad1}{Episode 7: "Meow Meow, Meow Meow, Meow Meow Meow Meow Meow?"}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.70,0:23:59.34,DefaultTop,Kuro,0,0,0,,{Yours is somewhere around the 6800s for \Ncommon family names in Japan, Ozu-san.}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.34,0:24:00.81,DefaultTop,Ozu,0,0,0,,{That's a shockamole!}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:00.81,0:24:03.02,DefaultTop,Kuro,0,0,0,,{A... shocka-what?}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.02,0:24:05.27,DefaultTop,Ozu,0,0,0,,{I'm saying it's a shock, obviously.}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:05.27,0:24:07.82,DefaultTop,Ozu,0,0,0,,{It's a regular holy guacamole \Nshockamole, you see.}
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.19,0:24:10.31,DefaultTop,Kuro,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry, could you speak Japanese?}
